Template: The menu bar button label for the template feature.
Insert template: The toolbar button tooltip for the template feature.
The main text of the message shown to the user when no templates are available in the template feature.
The main text of the message shown to the user when no templates are available for the search criteria.
Please try a different phrase or check t: The secondary text of the message shown to the user when no templates are available for the search criteria.
Search template: The label of the input allowing users to search templates.
%0 templates found: Aria status message indicating how many templates has been found using search templates input. Example: '%0 templates found'.
